"This guy's nothing special."

527
00:46:05,289 --> 00:46:08,000
The look I've seen
in their eyes many times.

528
00:46:08,084 --> 00:46:11,379
"This guy's nothing special.
How shall I break up with him?"

529
00:46:11,462 --> 00:46:13,256
"What excuse should I come up with?"

530
00:46:13,881 --> 00:46:16,342
