531
00:46:16,926 --> 00:46:18,636
"Yes, I know I'm nothing special."

532
00:46:18,720 --> 00:46:22,056
"But I'm fun to be around.
At least I'm not a bore."

533
00:46:22,140 --> 00:46:25,184
