what am I supposed to do?

534
00:46:25,268 --> 00:46:26,853
What else can I do
when they want to end it?

535
00:46:26,936 --> 00:46:29,188
From that point on,
I start fighting them constantly.

536
00:46:29,272 --> 00:46:32,024
And that's when the reason we broke up
becomes that I watched a movie alone,

537
00:46:32,108 --> 00:46:34,152
or that she texted some guy late at night.

538
00:46:34,235 --> 00:46:39,157
And it can never be because
she found out what a pathetic loser I am.

539
00:46:51,461 --> 00:46:52,420
I know it, too.

540
00:46:53,755 --> 00:46:56,966
That I'm not the best she can have.

541
00:47:01,387 --> 00:47:04,390
I know that she thinks she can
find someone better.

542
00:47:11,022 --> 00:47:14,192
<i>He always asked, "Aren't you
curious about my neighborhood?"</i>

543
00:47:15,026 --> 00:47:17,904
<i>"Aren't you curious about Dangmi Station?</i>

544
00:47:19,655 --> 00:47:21,157
<i>Tell him I know now.</i>

