554
00:48:34,355 --> 00:48:36,899
I'm not that rude usually.

555
00:48:41,362 --> 00:48:44,657
We should drink together sometime
and get to know each other.

556
00:48:49,620 --> 00:48:52,832
What should I call you?
I only know your last name.

557
00:48:57,211 --> 00:48:58,921
I was born in 1985…

558
00:49:06,053 --> 00:49:07,972
I'll just call you Gu.

559
00:50:11,035 --> 00:50:13,245
Did everyone just arrive?

560
00:50:13,788 --> 00:50:15,539
I worked overtime. I didn't drink.

561
00:50:19,460 --> 00:50:20,962
You're home.

562
00:50:42,201 --> 00:50:43,577
<i>If you think about it,</i>

563
00:50:44,703 --> 00:50:46,622
<i>all the assholes in my life</i>

564
00:50:47,331 --> 00:50:49,333
<i>started with that same look in their eyes.</i>

565
00:50:51,085 --> 00:50:52,628
<i>Eyes that seemed to say,</i>

566
00:50:53,378 --> 00:50:55,255
<i>"You're not good enough."</i>

567
00:51:00,177 --> 00:51:02,137
<i>It makes you feel so small.</i>

568
00:51:03,013 --> 00:51:05,182
<i>Like you're insignificant.</i>

569
00:51:07,059 --> 00:51:11,271
<i>It was that look
that made us sick and exhausted.</i>

570
00:51:13,065 --> 00:51:16,568
<i>Repetitive relationships you jump into
to find something to love about yourself,</i>

571
00:51:17,152 --> 00:51:21,323
