614
00:55:36,328 --> 00:55:38,413
I feel cramped and stifled.

615
00:55:41,541 --> 00:55:43,335
I want to break free.

616
00:55:47,631 --> 00:55:48,465
Liberation?

617
00:55:51,385 --> 00:55:52,469
I like it.

618
00:56:04,147 --> 00:56:05,565
The three of you?

619
00:56:07,025 --> 00:56:07,901
Yes.

620
00:56:10,904 --> 00:56:14,282
